node.text:
Taking my delicates to the dry cleaners? I don’t know her.
I’m all about at-home care for wool, cashmere and even silk with @thelaundress; not only is it less expensive and increases the life of my garments, but it’s much better for the environment.
Use TIKA25 for 25% off plant-based laundry and home cleaning products from The Laundress and a free Wash & Stain Bar with purchase of $25+

node.text:
New York Fashion Week outfit number 2! Just having a little moment in my custom @marcbouwer around the grand salon of the @baccarathotels before I head to the next show. The perfect dress to say ‘adieu’ to summer and ‘bonjour’ to autumn.
Dress by @marcbouwer
Shot at @baccarathotels

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by tika the iggy in New York City with @ashistudio, @tikatheiggy, and @globalfashioncollective.

node.text:
Off to my first @nyfw show! I felt right at home in the front row, thank you @globalfashioncollective for having me. 🤍
Wearing @ashistudio 
Tailored by @nicodesign.ca

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by tika the iggy in Chelsea Piers with @tikatheiggy, and @grig.paris. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text: Oh hi New York, you look happy to see me! Had the most wonderful day exploring the city, excited for my first @nyfw show tomorrow. 💞

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by tika the iggy in Montreal, Quebec with @oneplus, and @tikatheiggy.

node.text: Whoever said ‘less is more’ clearly didn’t have a lengthy neck like moi. #ShotonOnePlus @oneplus #ad

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by tika the iggy in Montreal, Quebec with @tea_you, and @tikatheiggy. May be an image of indoor.

node.text: Staring off into the void instead of packing for New York Fashion Week. So much clothing, so little suitcase…what’s a girl to do?! 🧳🛫🗽

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by tika the iggy in Montreal, Quebec with @tikatheiggy, and @shantell_design. May be an image of 1 person and animal.

node.text:
If you aren’t wearing long animal-print capes this autumn, then what are you doing?????
🤎 by @shantell_design

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by tika the iggy on August 30, 2021 tagging @lokopetapparel, and @tikatheiggy. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text: When I’m away at the cottage I always try to go incowgnito. 🐄
